而是最终说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/critics-praise-cobra-kai-finale-mr-miyagi-himself-would-be-proud-3837771">：“先生Miyagi本人会感到自豪”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cobra-kai-brought-back-pat-moritas-mr-miyagi-using-ai-3838133">“眼镜蛇Kai”帖子将Pat Morita的Miyagi先生带回了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
