54.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/CharliXCXClairo-Sofia-collaboration-Laneway-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/CharliXCXClairo-Sofia-collaboration-Laneway-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/CharliXCXClairo-Sofia-collaboration-Laneway-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/CharliXCXClairo-Sofia-collaboration-Laneway-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>已加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/clairo">Clairo</a>在澳大利亚的舞台上表演“索非亚”  - 查看下面的录像。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/clairo-charm-album-review-3774342">Clairo  - “魅力”评论：深入研究欲望</a></strong></li></ul><p>现场合作是在克莱罗（Clairo）在今天（2月14日）的墨尔本版<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laneway-2025-charli-xcx-clairo-and-beabadoobee-lead-line-up-3800843#:~:text=Laneway%202025%3A%20Charli%20XCX%2C%20Clairo%20and%20Beabadoobee%20lead%20line%2Dup,-Other%20acts%20include&amp;text=The%20first%20wave%20of%20artists,See%20the%20line%2Dup%20below.&amp;text=Today%20(October%209)%2C%20the%20long%2Drunning%20St.">2025年</a>墨尔本版的演出期间进行的。两位艺术家都参加了今年活动的阵容 - 该活动还访问了布里斯班，悉尼，阿德莱德和珀斯。</p><p>查理（Charli）分享了她的蒂克托克（Tiktok），克罗洛（Clairo）也与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a>在后台闲逛，并为“我的情人xx”加上了标题。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/clairo/2025/flemington-racecourse-melbourne-australia-43508347.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SetList.fm的</em></a>说法，“索非亚”的联合演绎是克罗洛的13轨巷道表演的近距离演出。这也标志着这首歌以来首次出现在2022年以来的列表中。</p><p>在舞台上一起跳舞，克罗洛和查理呼吁人群“向我们唱歌”。在这里观看当下的粉丝录像：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Clairo和Charli XCX在墨尔本一起演唱<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/CharmTourMelbourne?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">索非亚</a>的另一个视频<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f48c.png" alt="💌" class="wp-smiley